ODQ4MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1703883731.122929", "card_id": "Q_637238574", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 70}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一女子离职后把手机静音一年，表示找回了幸福感，手机一响就焦虑算精神工伤吗？生活与工作失去边界该怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据三联生活周刊：离职当天，一走出公司楼栋大门，女子就把手机调成了静音模式，世界安静了。那一刻，她等了好几年。女子称，「手机刚开始静音的日子，我还不习惯，时不时就习惯性拿起手机，划开屏幕，发现没有新信息，松一口气，继而想起，我已经离职了。大约半个月左右，我才戒掉隔一会儿看看手机的毛病，只是偶尔还会有幻听。有时是在炖汤，有时是在陪孩子做数独，恍惚就听见手机响，匆忙划开手机，没有新消息，然后想到是听错了，手机一直静音，不可能响的。我提着菜，慢慢晃回家，一点也不着急，那一路上，我有一种陌生的幸福感，无法形容。」 离职后，我把手机静音的这一年"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-694da9c4427adf353c933e10f43b27d5_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "42 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/637238574"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI6YXN0eOFrLI3EAMaCTEwMzg4NzA0NCCEi7msBjAAOKUBQB9yCTYzNzIzODU3NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1703883731.123583", "card_id": "Q_407155493", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 69}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "三国有哪些不被大众所熟知的冷知识？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cd64a16508a14c74ccc0ec3e8a332d56_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "42 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/407155493"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I6YXN0eOFrLI3EAMaCDUyNzU2MjEzINOBvfgFMAA42AFAIHIJNDA3MTU1NDkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1703883731.123832", "card_id": "Q_633760469", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在选 2024 的新年礼物，什么牌子的香水送给女朋友比较好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5a4c01cc0c0679c885a3b